OL,3,CWho is the new Welsh Secretary?
OL,5,FJo Stevens has been announced as the
OL,6,Fnew Secretary of State for Wales.
OL,8,FThe Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Fappointed MPs to his cabinet on Friday
OL,10,Fafternoon after Labour's landslide
OL,11,Fvictory in general election.
OL,13,FMs Stevens has been shadow Wales
OL,14,Fsecretary since 2021.
OL,16,FThe role of Welsh Secretary is
OL,17,Fdesigned to make sure Wales is
OL,18,Fproperly represented when significant
OL,19,Fdecisions are made by the UK
OL,20,FGovernment.
