OL,3,CWho is the new Welsh Secretary?
OL,5,FBut who is the latest incumbent of the
OL,6,Frole?
OL,8,FBorn in 1966, Ms Stevens was educated
OL,9,Fin Flintshire before going on to study
OL,10,Fat Manchester University where she
OL,11,Fgraduated in 1988.
OL,13,FShe went on to have a career as a
OL,14,Fsolicitor, something she pursued for
OL,15,Fmore than 25 years.
OL,17,FHowever she then embarked on a career
OL,18,Fchange, deciding to stand for
OL,19,Fparliament, and became the MP for
OL,20,FCardiff Central in 2015.
