OL,3,CWho is the new Welsh Secretary?
OL,5,FFollowing boundary changes she now
OL,6,Frepresents the Cardiff East
OL,7,Fconstituency, which comprises part of
OL,8,Fthe old Cardiff Central, Cardiff South
OL,9,Fand Penarth constituencies.
OL,11,FMs Stevens has been a Labour Party
OL,12,Fmember and activist for more than 30
OL,13,Fyears and is part of the GMB Union as
OL,14,Fwell as the Union of Shop,
OL,15,FDistributive and Allied Workers.
OL,17,FDescribing herself as an
OL,18,Finternationalist, she has paid
OL,19,Fparticular attention to human rights
OL,20,Fissues in Colombia, being an active
OL,21,Fmember of the Justice for Colombia NGO.
