OL,3,CWho is the new Welsh Secretary?
OL,5,FCloser to home, Ms Stevens is said to
OL,6,Fbe a big sports fan, and is a regular
OL,7,Fat the Cardiff City stadium to cheer
OL,8,Fon the Bluebirds as well as on the
OL,9,Fterraces of the Cardiff Blues.
OL,11,FIn her spare time she's said to enjoy
OL,12,Fsampling real ale as well as reading
OL,13,Fand listening to music.
OL,15,FReacting to her appointment Ms Stevens
OL,16,Fsaid, "it is a real privilege to be
OL,17,Fappointed to the Office of the
OL,18,FSecretary of State for Wales and to
OL,19,Fserve in Prime Minister Keir Starmer's
OL,20,Ffirst Cabinet.
