OL,3,CWho is the new Welsh Secretary?
OL,5,F"Wales has a crucial role to play in
OL,6,Fpowering the UK's national renewal,
OL,7,Fcontributing to our energy security
OL,8,Fand the industries that will deliver a
OL,9,Fprosperous future.
OL,11,F"My absolute priority is to deliver
OL,12,Ffor Wales and work with the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment to stabilise the economy,
OL,14,Fdrive investment and create jobs.
OL,16,F"As a result of our plans, people
OL,17,Facross Wales will share in that
OL,18,Fprosperity and we will tackle
OL,19,Fdeprivation and poverty together."
