OL,3,CWho is the new Welsh Secretary?
OL,5,F"Under my leadership the Wales Office
OL,6,Fwill once again be a steadfast
OL,7,Fadvocate for Wales from within the UK
OL,8,FGovernment, ensuring that Wales's
OL,9,Fneeds are prioritised, and its voice
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,F"I am determined to reset the
OL,13,Frelationship between the UK and Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment. We will co-operate and
OL,15,Fwork together to deliver better
OL,16,Fresults for people in Wales.
OL,18,F"I am honoured to serve Wales and its
OL,19,Fpeople and bring about the change that
OL,20,Four new government has promised."
