OL,3,CWho is the new Welsh Secretary?
OL,5,FMs Stevens is said to have started a
OL,6,Ffull programme of meetings, briefings,
OL,7,Fand visits to begin delivering the new
OL,8,Fgovernment's agenda for Wales.
OL,10,FUntil now the position of Welsh
OL,11,FSecretary has often been one of
OL,12,Fconflict with the Welsh Government
OL,13,Fwhich regularly complains Wales is
OL,14,Funable to prosper as it should due to
OL,15,Ffunding cuts.
OL,17,FMs Stevens' role will be different to
OL,18,Fher predecessor with both governments
OL,19,Fin Cardiff Bay and Westminster being
OL,20,Fcontrolled by Labour.
